</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="go">Запишем 2 как два
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="go">Сейчас будний день
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="go">Еще нет двенадцати
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="go">Я bool
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="go">Я int
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="go">Неизвестный тип string</span></span></span></code></pre>
          </td>
        </tr>
        
